data.title: Kenneth 'Babyface' Edmonds
data.meta_description: Kenneth 'Babyface' Edmonds. Soundtrack: Ghostbusters 2. Kenneth Brian Edmonds better known by his stage name Babyface, is an American singer, songwriter, and record producer. He has written and produced over 26 number-one R&B hits throughout his career and has won 12 Grammy Awards. He was ranked number 20 on NME's 50 of The Greatest Producers Ever list.
